# Keep host build outputs and dependencies out of the image build context, so
# container builds are reproducible and match CI. A stale host `dist/` copied in
# would mask a broken in-image build (exactly what hid the web Dockerfile's missing
# packages build until the container-smoke job — ADR-0052 — ran on a clean checkout).
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.expo
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log
.git
.github
